Reginald Barlow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reginald_Barlow 0 Reginald Harry Barlow (June 17, 1866 – July 6, 1943) was a veteran stage and screen character actor, author, and film director. He was a busy performer in Hollywood films of the 1930s. Reginald_Harry_Barlow ( June_17 , 1866 – July_6_,_1943 ) was a_veteran_stage_and_screen_character_actor , author , and film_director .
